{
  "_doc": "Cogito-color steerability prompts. Each prompt is a fill-in-the-blank designed to elicit a single color word as the next token. ground_truth_color is the canonical name, expected_top_token is the no-intervention completion we'd expect cogito to score highly. Prompts are organised by HSV axis they probe: HUE_* sweep hue at high sat/val; SAT_* sweep saturation; VAL_* sweep value. ACHROMATIC entries cover the gray axis. Each prompt has a non-empty leading space on the expected token to match BPE conventions.",
  "scale_unit_doc": "alpha is in per-axis-std units. Each axis A is unit-normed; in cogito_intervene.py we multiply by sigma_A = std(X @ A) measured on the harvest so alpha=1 = 1-sigma push along that direction.",
